Create a Flask-based REST API with the following specification:

Endpoint:
- /task
  - Methods: GET, POST
  - Data model:
    - title: string
    - due_date: date (YYYY-MM-DD)
    - is_done: boolean

Requirements:
- Use Flask and SQLAlchemy for the API.
- Include Swagger documentation using the flasgger library.
- Add YAML-style docstrings for each endpoint to support Swagger UI.
- Ensure the API is functional and uses appropriate HTTP status codes.
